title: fooBillard v1.3
description:
fooBillard is 3D billiards game with realistic high quality graphics and realistic ball physics (also jump shots).

Features:

* Pool
* Speed-Pool-Game (pot nine balls as fast as possible)
* Snooker
* AI-opponent (5 different levels)
* network opponent (IP/port)
* 2nd human opponent (pass along)
* full AI-Tournament
* registering hiscores online for speed-pool
* dummy/expert mode (with/without helper lines)
** scoring/ranking is only possible in expert mode

What's New:

improved ball menu
fixed some viewer placing bugs
added cue
cue cannot intersect with balls and table borders
=> offset/angle will automatically adjust accordingly
added homepage (foobillard.org)
added dummy/expert mode (helper lines)
added table lines
